      "writtenOn": "2018-06-20T17:03:23Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "even worse, if we want to have interoperability between different platforms in the emulator the only way to get it is to open all files on Windows as binary, even the ones with text. Otherwise a file created on Windows will only be readable on Windows, and copying it into Mac/Linux will result in emulator not being able to parse it correctly.",
