      "writtenOn": "2018-06-20T17:13:55Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Yeah, text mode vs binary mode :)\n\nIs it safe to open intended-as-text files as binary on Windows though? I see we are using it for parsing GPU info and protobufs and actual text files so far. *Something about wchar_t and stuff*",
